# AWS File Upload Gallery

A file upload and gallery website hosted on AWS.

## Architecture
- EC2 (Ubuntu) — hosts the web server
- Apache — serves HTTP requests
- Flask (Python) — backend logic
- S3 — file storage
- IAM Role — secure EC2 to S3 access

## Features
- Upload any file from browser
- Files stored in AWS S3
- Gallery view of all uploaded files
- Presigned URLs for secure file access

## AWS Services Used
- EC2
- S3
- IAM
- VPC
- Security Groups
- Route Tables
- Internet Gateway
